OL,5,
OL,6,CG2021FThe final of Euro 2020 airs on
OL,7,FBBC One and ITV. England v Italy. Italy
OL,8,Fwon on penalties. The combined audience
OL,9,Fis 29.85 million viewers (24.2m BBC and
OL,10,F5.6m ITV). At the time, this was the
OL,11,Ffourth most-watched TV special event in
OL,12,FUK history.
